=============================================
Delete:

>>> H = {101: "Madhan", 102: "Mohan", 103: "Reddy"}
>>> del(H[103]) 
>>> H
{101: 'Madhan', 102: 'Mohan'}
>>> H.keys()  @keys to dispaly
dict_keys([101, 102])


