****While Loop******

while 1==1:
	print("Hello All!")

Output:
Hello All!
Hello All!
Hello All!
Hello All!
Continus Printing:
-------------------------------------

name = ""
while len(name)==0:
    name = input("Enter the name:")
print("Hello",name)

Output:
Enter the name:
Enter the name:
Enter the name:
Enter the name:
Enter the name:Hello
Hello Hello


        (or)

name = None
while not name:
    name = input("Enter the name:")
print("Hello",name)


Output:
Enter the name:
Enter the name:
Enter the name:
Enter the name:
Enter the name:Hello
Hello Hello


